[SPEAKER_00]: Meanwhile, local boards of health have done a lot.

50
00:04:23,851 --> 00:04:32,692
[SPEAKER_00]: Local boards led the campaign for smoke-free workplace law two decades ago against extreme pushback, especially from restaurants and bars.

51
